                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On August 30, Secretary Acheson made a statement before the Senate Appropriations
                    Committee on the subject of additional funds needed for the Mutual Defense
                    Assistance Program. The text, released to the press on the same date, is printed
                    in the Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, September 11, 1950,
                    page 437.</p>
            </div>
